This was a great make-ahead recipe for a 50th anniversary party. I served it with a beef tenderloin with cabernet sauce and it was a good combination. The marinade of the chicken was wonderful, and the sicilian olives in the salad adds a great punch to the salad. Followed the recipe exactly, and proportions were great.

